title: main - help
text: ky!Help <optional tag> || Shows all availible help commands. Following the command with a tag prunes the embed for all commands that fit the tag.

title: main - about
text: ky!about || Displays Kanade Bot about embed

title: arcade - ealinks
text: ky!ealinks || Displays various important e-amusement links

title: iidx - exscore
text: ky!exscore <Total Notes> || Calculates the EXSCORE amount necesary to get MAX, AAA, AA, or A from a songs total notes.

title: iidx - iidxdansp
text: ky!iidxdansp <class-section> || displays IIDX class courses per section. (SP) Valid Arguments: kyu, dan, and den

title: iidx - iidxdandp
text: ky!iidxdandp <class-section> || displays IIDX class courses per section. (DP) Valid Arguments: kyu, dan, and den

title: sdvx - sdvxdan
text: ky!sdvxdan <skill-level> || Displays SDVX SKILL ANALYZER courses per skill level. Valid Arguments: 1 - 11 and inf

title: sdvx - vf
text: ky!vf <First 4 of score> <PUC, UC, etc.> <difficulty> || Determines Volforce by user provided values.

title: arcade - remywiki
text: ky!remywiki <search term> || Searches RemyWiki and links it to channel used

title: arcade - playsleft
text: ky!playsleft <number of credits> || Sends how many plays left you have on 8 credit rhythm game based on user input.

title: sdvx - sdvxtier
text: ky!sdvxtier || Sends link for SDVX clear tierlist

title: main - gacha
text: ky!gacha || Sends a random response

title: arcade - verify
text: ky!verify <Attached Image>|| Submits rhythm game score for role verification.

title: admin - boost
text: ky!boost || Creates a txt file listing all current server boosters

title: admin - bonk
text: ky!bonk <user-mention> || Sends mentioned user to horny jail

title: admin - unbonk
text: ky!unbonk <user-mention> || Removes mentioned user to horny jail

title: admin - copy
text: ky!copy || counts every message sent in every channel (Lolzep Only)

title: admin - memberupdate
text: ky!memberupdate || Updates the member count.

title: admin - forceabout
text: kyt!forceabout || Forces public facing ky!about while in debug mode.

title: admin - noresponse
text: ky!noresponse || Disables bot responses in all channels for 30 mins.

title: admin - restart
text: ky!restart || Restarts Kanade Bot

title: admin - gitpull
text: ky!gitpull || pulls latest git commit
